name: Drawing of Madness / 2018
description: Surrealistrasyon/Şerif Gümüşbaş/Pencil color drawing/1800x2700pixel/I try to understand and observe our emotions and feelings at critical moments with my drawings. You can think of it as a description of the pain of metamorphosis, anger, despair, insolvency, madness, borderline feeling, moment of losing control, and so on./Drawing is an enjoyable way to express myself and reflect on what I have been expressing. The automatism method I discovered over time has been the best tool for describing ..
